metadata.name: God of Durian
metadata.description:
In a deep and peaceful forest among the flora and fauna that inhabit the forest. In the middle of this deep forest lies a statue of a god of help and fertility.

No one knows who this god is. They only knew that every time this deity came to help or meet. will see him eating durian deliciously called "God of Durian"

Over time, people have been told from generation to generation. Later, a statue of him was made on the advice of the elders. And whenever the villagers have to go to ask for blessings in the forest They will worship durians and ask them to take care of them. and bestow abundance
